1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:58,688 --> 00:01:01,079
(Song Group)

4
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:03,119
Have you found the cause
of the accident?

5
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:05,959
According to the investigation,

6
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:08,879
the accident occurred
due to substandard building materials.

7
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,560
It led to the wall's collapse.

8
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,040
Who is the person in charge?

9
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,719
Well...

10
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,280
Just give me an answer directly.

11
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,439
Stop stammering.

12
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:25,280
Wansheng took up
the nursing home project.

13
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,920
According to Mr. Li,

14
00:01:27,392 --> 00:01:30,336
the project manager was Ji Xuan.

15
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,519
- Miss Ji?
- Yes.

16
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,159
The workplace
despises baseless speculation.

17
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,079
If you have proof, present it.

18
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:48,319
This is Miss Ji's account
ending in 8812.

19
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,439
It received a payment.

20
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:53,000
(Cross-border transfer: 1.5 million yuan)
1.5 million from an overseas account.

21
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:56,040
The payment note says nursing home.

22
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:02,599
Impossible!

23
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:06,359
Ji Xuan lined her own pockets.

24
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,439
This severely damages
the group's interests.

25
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:10,599
She cannot remain at Song Group.

26
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:33,840
Ji Xuan.

27
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,680
Ji Xuan.

28
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,719
I need to talk to you.

29
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:50,840
Ji Xuan.

30
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:55,520
You've betrayed my trust in you.

31
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:58,360
Chairman, I didn't do this.

32
00:02:58,439 --> 00:03:00,240
I don't know where this money came from.

33
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:03,080
I can overlook this matter.

34
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,759
But on one condition:

35
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,000
you must leave Song Zhaoli

36
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,000
and Song Group.

37
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:11,639
Chairman, I haven't used this bank card
for a long time.

38
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,319
I really...

39
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,960
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

40
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,199
Ji Xuan, I have good news for you.

41
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:22,520
Someone reviewed your profile
and decided to sponsor your education.

42
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:25,800
Could you give me
his contact information?

43
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,960
I'd like to thank him.

44
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,280
He funded you anonymously.

45
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,560
He only left an email address.

46
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,360
He said you could reach him via email.

47
00:03:31,776 --> 00:03:32,360
Okay.

48
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,639
Please send it to me later.

49
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,560
Thank you, Mr. Zhang. Thank you.

50
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:42,528
(Income: 20,000 yuan.
Note: tuition and living expenses)

51
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:55,120
This card was used
during my university years.

52
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,039
It was from Song Zhaoli.

53
00:03:57,536 --> 00:04:00,576
You found his account to frame me,
didn't you?

54
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,680
Song Zhaoli's back

55
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,039
is covered in marks from your beating.

56
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,560
I have a question.

57
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:12,768
Why do you treat Song Zhaoli like this?

58
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:17,024
Before Shaoqian passed away,

59
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,560
Song Zhaoli
was just an illegitimate child.

60
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,519
He got lucky.

61
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,720
When it was his time to die,

62
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,759
he didn't die.

63
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,839
Unexpectedly,

64
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:31,240
he ended up becoming the sole heir

65
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,959
of the Song family.

66
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,879
You use him,

67
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,920
yet you despise him.

68
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:44,839
Is this your magnanimity and vision?

69
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:55,199
I won't accept this ridiculous frame-up.

70
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,639
I will pursue legal action.

71
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,800
The one who should stay away
from Song Zhaoli is you, not me.

72
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:03,759
From now on,
I'll be the one to love Song Zhaoli.

73
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,920
You can't even find a kidney donor
for your mom.

74
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,680
What capability do you have to love him?

75
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:16,279
Only by leaving Song Zhaoli
and Song Group

76
00:05:17,088 --> 00:05:20,192
can your mom's surgery proceed.

77
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,079
Think it over.

78
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:25,120
Between Song Zhaoli and your mom,

79
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,720
you can only choose one.

80
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,360
I'm sorry, Xuan.

81
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:41,439
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

82
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,180
Sorry, we couldn't stop him.

83
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,439
I'm sorry, Song Zhaoli.

84
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:04,839
What did you say to her?

85
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:08,160
I told her to choose

86
00:06:08,864 --> 00:06:10,080
between you and her mom.

87
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:13,600
She clearly didn't choose you.

88
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,079
You're despicable.

89
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,360
It seems

90
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:22,240
you've been away from me for so long

91
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,839
that you've forgotten my rules.

92
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:25,639
Someone!

93
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,199
- Yes.
- Yes.

94
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,360
Send him home.

95
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,120
Shaoqian,

96
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,376
if only you were

97
00:07:06,432 --> 00:07:07,560
still alive.

98
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,519
Song Zhaoli.

99
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,120
What is this?

100
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,600
Grandfather.

101
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,079
Now,

102
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,319
you pose no threat to me whatsoever.

103
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,600
Song Zhaoli,

104
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,920
you are just an illegitimate child.

105
00:07:42,208 --> 00:07:45,184
Without Song Group, you are nothing.

106
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,600
I was treated differently

107
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:50,759
because my mom
wasn't legally married in?

108
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:55,120
Back then, I brought you back home

109
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:57,600
just to contain the scandal.

110
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,079
The one who should have died
in the kidnapping

111
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,600
was you,

112
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:05,480
not Shaoqian.

113
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,519
Tomorrow afternoon, they will drive out.

114
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:15,920
Make it clean.

115
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:18,040
Don't let Shaoqian get hurt.

116
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,480
Today,

117
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,519
only one of you two will live.

118
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,759
You decide.

119
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,299
Shaoqian.

120
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,320
Zhaoli.

121
00:09:01,664 --> 00:09:02,208
Shaoqian.

122
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,460
Shaoqian.

123
00:09:04,672 --> 00:09:05,344
Shaoqian.

124
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,816
Shaoqian.

125
00:09:07,264 --> 00:09:08,224
Shaoqian.

126
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,639
You caused Shaoqian's death.

127
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,679
You've grown up now.

128
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:22,480
I can't threaten you.

129
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:25,279
But I can threaten Ji Xuan.

130
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,879
As long as I'm alive,

131
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:32,639
she'll never find a kidney donor.

132
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,200
Sorry to disappoint you, Grandpa.

133
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,720
The report shows

134
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,919
I'm a highly compatible match
for Ji Xuan's mom.

135
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,799
I've decided to donate my kidney to her.

136
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,559
You're insane!

137
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,240
From today onwards,

138
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,840
I'm no longer part of this family.

139
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,200
Without me,

140
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:55,240
Song Group will soon be swallowed up.

141
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,792
You will be alone

142
00:09:57,952 --> 00:09:59,440
for the rest of your life.

143
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,120
Mom.

144
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:11,639
Xuan, what happened?

145
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,919
Don't cry.

146
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:13,779
Mom.

147
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:16,200
It's over between Song Zhaoli and me.

148
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,200
What? What happened?

149
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,679
Tell me.

150
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:24,960
Ji Xuan.

151
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:33,159
I thought I'd never see you again.

152
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,440
That won't happen.

153
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:38,519
- Prepare for the surgery.
- Yes, Mr. Song.

154
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,320
(To find a kidney donor,)

155
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:45,120
(he also underwent tests,)

156
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,879
(preparing to give his kidney)

157
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,639
(to your mom.)

158
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,879
Are you going to donate your own kidney?

159
